DAY 1:

Initialized Project
→ npm init -y

Installed Packages
→ npm i express ejs

Required Modules & Created App
→ require('express'), require('path'), etc.

Started the Server
→ app.listen(3000, ...)

Set the View Engine
→ app.set('view engine', 'ejs')

Created views/ Folder with index.ejs
→ Wrote basic HTML like "Hello World"

Rendered the Page
→ Used res.render('index') inside a route

